</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-24_ pf-text-1">The CAA regulates all civil aviation activities within the UK, including airlines, airports, air traffic services, and general aviation.

</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-26_ pf-text-1">In 2022, UK airlines carried over 250 million passengers, all regulated under CAA's stringent safety protocols.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-28_ pf-text-1">The CAA actively works to mitigate the environmental impact of aviation, including noise and emissions control.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-30_ pf-text-1">The aviation industry contributes significantly to the UK economy, supporting over 230,000 jobs directly and indirectly.








